{"tid":1606004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警察疑智障人士都唔放過","createTime":"2019-09-30T12:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:26:15.000Z","uid":222599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d6add9a397d784707ad8601359e9a427e56825","tid":1606004,"uid":222599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"網上流傳片段，在速龍小隊搜捕示威者期間，警員截查一名疑似唐氏綜合症男患者，並將他按到鐵閘上；該男子被警員截查時明顯受驚。速龍小隊警員及後將該男子制服地上，男子不斷呼叫求饒，「媽咪啊！媽咪啊！唔好啊！」速龍小隊其後令他提供身份證明文件，該男子跪在地上，再求饒道「對唔住啊！」<br />\n<br />\n一名社工表明身份，希望上前協助該神情慌張的男子，但被速龍小隊警員喝止，「攞咩名啊！走！走！」<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/925224541187133/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F925224541187133%2F&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6nWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=7f5f2fc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/925224541187133/</a>"},{"pid":"ec3bfd23a2b040b5b032f494a92e9586bd5bddad","tid":1606004,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:25:22.000Z","msg":"pi"},{"pid":"a3b95f623fe770230753a6c34dcb1951f02edef1","tid":1606004,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:26:15.000Z","msg":"IT仔嚟"}]}